# [ORG_SLUG]-universe

Central repository for the [ORG_SLUG] software ecosystem: architecture,
governance, application inventory, host inventory.

## What's here

- **CLAUDE.md** — read first if you're an AI agent (operational protocol §0)
- **docs/governance/** — LGPD, naming, DNS, retention rules
- **docs/diagrams/** — C4, deployment, DFD diagrams (drawio files)
- **applications/** — one folder per app
- **hosts/** — one folder per production host
- **.universe.json** — metadata (org, registered apps)

## How to use as a developer

When working on any project of [ORG_SLUG]:
1. Run `/rsct-setup` in that project (installs governance protocol)
2. Run `/rsct-canonical-source` (wires the project's CLAUDE.md to this universe)

## How to use as an AI agent

Read CLAUDE.md first. Never fetch remote artifacts without user OK
(see §0 in CLAUDE.md).

